name: Nova's Whisper
description: Jahoda's outfit. Adopting a new look is the first step toward bidding farewell to the past. The clothes from this ensemble were custom-made at the behest of Jahoda's dearest, most brilliant, wisest, and all-knowingest boss, Nefer, while the goggles were a gift from Aino, and the hood was hand-made by Ineffa.
